-------------------------------------------------------
[spell]: Enchant Weapon
[level]: 7th Lvl Enchantment
[cost] : 160 sp
[type] : alteration
[delay]: none
-------------------------------------------------------
This critical spell will enhance the killing powers
of any weapon.  The spell can only be cast a single
time on the same weapon.  The spell is permanent
unless the weapon breaks or the spell is cancelled.
Use the command 'endenchant' to cancel the spell.
-------------------------------------------------------

